  "body": "Frame an increasingly common wallet has a local RPC available on localhost:1248, previous versions of forge script would send via the provider and it handle signing, now however it has been updated to include an explict set of accounts to sign via as detailed in the below comment.\r\n\r\nForge create and cast send all execute via the provider directly so it stands to reason this should be included inside the forge script execution flow as well\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/ae3ec74234fe30a88279b3850c99ff191f373781/crates/cli/src/opts/wallet/multi_wallet.rs#L66",
